---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about PureVida Water Technologies, founded by Payton Fedell. Delivering premium bottleless water solutions to Texas businesses since day one."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
          About PureVida
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-300">
          Pure water, full service, zero hassle.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Statement -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            PureVida Water Technologies exists to transform how Texas businesses think about workplace hydration. We combine cutting-edge filtration technology with white-glove service to deliver an experience that's better for your team, your budget, and the environment.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            From small offices to large industrial facilities, we provide the same level of care and attention to every client. Because when it comes to the water your team drinks every day, there should be no compromise.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sky-500">1,100+</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Businesses Served</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sky-500">3</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Metro Areas</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sky-500">99%</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Customer Retention</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sky-500">24hr</div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">Response Time</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <img
              src="/images/team/payton-fedell.jpg"
              alt="Payton Fedell, Founder & CEO of PureVida Water Technologies"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative element -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-48 h-48 bg-sky-500/10 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-32 h-32 bg-sky-500/10 rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div>
          <p class="text-sky-500 font-semibold mb-2">Founder & CEO</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Payton Fedell</h2>

          <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-600">
            <p>
              I started PureVida Water Technologies from scratch with a simple belief: Texas businesses deserve better than the status quo of bottled water delivery.
            </p>
            <p>
              After seeing countless companies struggle with unreliable deliveries, heavy jugs, mounting costs, and growing piles of plastic waste, I knew there had to be a better way. So I built one.
            </p>
            <p>
              Today, PureVida serves over 1,100 businesses across Dallas-Fort Worth, Austin, and San Antonio. But our mission remains the same as day one: provide the purest water, the best equipment, and service that actually shows up when you need it.
            </p>
            <p>
              Every installation, every service call, every filter changeâ€”we treat your business like it's our own. Because at the end of the day, your trust is everything.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Signature -->
          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
            <svg class="h-16 w-auto text-gray-800" viewBox="0 0 200 60" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M10 45 Q15 20 25 35 T40 30 Q50 25 55 40 L60 35 Q65 45 75 30 T90 35" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M95 40 Q100 25 110 35 T125 30 L130 40" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <path d="M135 35 Q140 45 150 30 T165 40 Q175 35 185 45" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Payton Fedell</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Founder & CEO, PureVida Water Technologies</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">What Drives Us</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-600">The principles behind everything we do</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-2xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Uncompromising Quality</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            We only partner with manufacturers who meet our rigorous standards. Every system we install is built to last and backed by our service guarantee.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-2xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Service-First Mentality</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Equipment is only as good as the service behind it. Our local technicians respond fast, solve problems right, and treat your space with respect.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-sky-100 text-sky-600 rounded-2xl mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Environmental Responsibility</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Every bottleless system eliminates hundreds of plastic bottles annually. We're proud to help our clients reduce their environmental footprint.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Ready to Partner with PureVida?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xl text-gray-300">
        Join over 1,100 Texas businesses who trust us with their workplace hydration.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <button data-trial-modal class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-sky-500 hover:bg-sky-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg transition shadow-lg cursor-pointer">
          Request Your Free Trial
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
